Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變回原樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:04.53,title1,NTP,0,0,200,,{\fad(500,500)}第９回
